subject: Dog Sledding
Iditarod Trail Sled Dog Race (Alaska)
Westminster Kennel Club Dog Show
Dogs
lead_paragraph: A Siberian husky in the Westminster Kennel Club Dog Show, which begins Monday, is the descendant of an overlooked hero of the 1925 race to deliver lifesaving diphtheria serum to icebound Nome, Alaska.
